oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Knight, John
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Summary: A campus tour of Florida State University, shot on April 26, 1969 is from 0:00 to 3:24. The Great Westcott Fire on April 27, 1969 is from 3:25 to 6:45. Wakulla Springs shot on May 9, 1969 in from 6:46 to 7:56. Footage of FSU's Flying High Circus starts at 7:57 and completes the video.
